{"tid":2209024,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗獲得IFFHS2019年國際比賽最佳射手獎","createTime":"2020-09-19T10:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T14:12:19.000Z","uid":173952,"like":5,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"f2d838a646b811ce4eef5a5b8edab73c14099e0d","tid":2209024,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:50:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cnASxYz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcnASxYz.png&h=60ef3f79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2019年入左21球<br />\n這次C朗第5次獲獎<br />\n是所有球員中最多<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當年歐偉倫都入過榜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n世界最佳神射手<br />\n歐偉倫曾經在2003年東亞足球錦標賽中一共射入7球，一度成為由IFFHS（國際足球歷史與統計協會）公佈的2003世界最佳神射手（統計每名球員在一年內的國家隊 A 級賽事的進球數目與球會在各項國際性賽事的進球數目）第一位，一度壓倒取得8個進球的西班牙國腳，效力皇家馬德里的魯爾，最後他以10個進球名列射手榜第9位"},{"pid":"857c958497a1a31f7771bb71816085d212c32d2d","tid":2209024,"uid":14126,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:55:07.000Z","msg":"收爺啦7頭 日撚日係到美斯牙朗"},{"pid":"c099d7ef464258adc6f43553f475cc2ebf3e8104","tid":2209024,"uid":90515,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T12:09:03.000Z","msg":"Ronaldo: Golden Shoe better than the Ballon d'Or<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.goal.com/en/news/722/la-liga/2015/10/17/16407602/ronaldo-golden-shoe-better-than-the-ballon-do\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.goal.com%2Fen%2Fnews%2F722%2Fla-liga%2F2015%2F10%2F17%2F16407602%2Fronaldo-golden-shoe-better-than-the-ballon-do&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=63c13b5d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.goal.com/en/news/722/la-liga/2015/10/17/16407602/ronaldo-golden-shoe-better-than-the-ballon-do</a><br />\n<br />\n&quot;I really love this award. It is the best award out there for me. Others can pick you as the best player, but an attacker's job is to make goals and I love that. I cannot deny that 